    - e.g. `/subscriptions/xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx/resourceGroups/xxxxxxxxxx/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualHubs/xxxxxxxxx/hubRouteTables/defaultRouteTable`
